<p>We collect data to provide the services you request. The data we collect can include the following:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and other contact details.</li>
    <li><strong>Appointment Information:</strong> Details about your appointments, including date, time, and the dentist you are seeing.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the data we collect for the following purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>To provide and manage your appointments.</li>
    <li>To communicate with you about your appointments and other services.</li>
    <li>To improve our services and develop new features.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
<p>We do not share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to provide our services or as required by law.</p>

<h2>Security of Your Information</h2>
<p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.</p>

